--- Pacifix / Scattershot / Afterburner / Nosecone ---

Scattershot, Afterburner and Nosecone menader towards the the 
storage bay, and join their fellow Technobots. They wait for Pacifix 
to start.

Pacifix glances around the group. He checks to see if everyone 
has arrived so he can begin.
